The fast food giant used its McDonald's Australia MyMaccas app for the giveaway. CAPE TOWN – Burger lovers in Australia were treated to free Big Macs on Monday to mark International Burger Day. The free Big Macs were available from 11am, with one free burger available for every customer. The fast food giant used its McDonald's Australia MyMaccas app for the giveaway. Locally, McDonald’s South Africa teamed up with local radio station 947 to share fun facts on International Burger Day.  (Edited by Shimoney Regter)